<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>A SocketException is thrown whenever a socket error is occurred in runtime.</para>

<para>You may even call the constructor with the FD of the socket and let JPL retrieve the last error code and its meaning via _utils:_GetLastError() and _utils::_GetLastErrorAsString</para>

